ald%20Trump%20said%20on%20Sunday%20he%20thinks%20Vice%20President%20Kamala%20Harris%20will%20be%20easier%20to%20defeat%20in%20November's%20election%20than%20Democratic%20President%20Joe%20Biden%2C%20who%20earlier%20in%20the%20day%20stepped%20aside%20as%20his%20party's%20candidate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHarris%20will%20be%20easier%20to%20beat%20than%20Joe%20Biden%20would%20have%20been%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20told%20CNN.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20and%20his%20campaign%20later%20also%20attacked%20Biden%20and%20Harris%20on%20social%20media%20while%20saying%20Biden%20was%20unfit%20to%20continue%20serving%20as%20president.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBiden%20ended%20his%20reelection%20campaign%20on%20Sunday%20after%20fellow%20Democrats%20lost%20faith%20in%20his%20mental%20acuity%20and%20ability%20to%20beat%20Trump.%20Biden%20endorsed%20Harris%20to%20replace%20him%20as%20the%20party's%20candidate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBiden%20had%20faced%20growing%20doubts%20about%20his%20reelection%20chances%20after%20a%20weak%20and%20faltering%20performance%20in%20a%20televised%20debate%20against%20Trump%20late%20last%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20his%20Truth%20Social%20platform%20on%20Sunday%2C%20Trump%20said%20Biden%20%26quot%3Bwas%20not%20fit%20to%20run%20for%20President%2C%20and%20is%20certainly%20not%20fit%20to%20serve.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20top%20Republicans%2C%20including%20House%20of%20Representatives%20Speaker%20Mike%20Johnson%2C%20also%20said%20Biden%20was%20not%20fit%20to%20serve%20as%20president%20and%20finish%20his%20term%20if%20he%20was%20stepping%20aside%20as%20the%20Democratic%20presidential%20candidate.%20Johnson%20explicitly%20called%20on%20Biden%20to%20resign.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%2C%20in%20a%20post%20on%20his%20Truth%20Social%20platform%2C%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BWe%20will%20suffer%20greatly%20because%20of%20his%20(Biden's)%20presidency%2C%20but%20we%20will%20remedy%20the%20damage%20he%20has%20done%20very%20quickly.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E