2%3A%22%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22RAJAT%20PANDIT%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fdelhi%2Findia-finalizes-plan-to-upgrade-sukhoi-30mki-fighter-jets-with-advanced-capabilities%2Farticleshow%2F111910699.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Explained%3A%20Joe%20Biden%20Won't%20Run%20For%20Re-Election.%20What%20Happens%20Next%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EUS%20President%20Joe%20Biden's%20decision%20Sunday%20to%20withdraw%20from%20the%20presidential%20race%20at%20such%20a%20late%20date%20--%20just%20over%20100%20days%20until%20the%20November%205%20election%20--%20is%20unprecedented%20in%20modern%20US%20electoral%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20coming%20days%2C%20Biden's%20fellow%20Democrats%20%26quot%3Bwill%20undertake%20a%20transparent%20and%20orderly%20process%20to%20move%20forward%20as%20a%20united%20Democratic%20Party%20with%20a%20candidate%20who%20can%20defeat%20Donald%20Trump%20in%20November%2C%26quot%3B%20chairman%20Jaime%20Harrison%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere's%20a%20look%20at%20how%20replacing%20the%2081-year-old%20could%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EChaotic%20convention%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20designate%20a%20formal%20nominee%2C%20delegates%20chosen%20from%20all%2050%20states%2C%20the%20US%20capital%20and%20overseas%20territories%20attend%20their%20party's%20summer%20nominating%20convention%20to%20officially%20anoint%20a%20candidate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBiden%20overwhelmingly%20won%20the%20primary%20votes%2C%20and%20the%20party's%20roughly%203%2C900%20delegates%20heading%20to%20the%20convention%20--%20scheduled%20to%20begin%20August%2019%20in%20Chicago%20--%20are%20pledged%20to%20back%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParty%20leaders%20had%20previously%20planned%20to%20formally%20nominate%20Biden%20via%20a%20virtual%20roll%20call%20ahead%20of%20the%20convention%2C%20due%20to%20potential%20legal%20issues%20regarding%20Ohio.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20Biden%20exiting%2C%20it%20is%20unclear%20if%20or%20when%20that%20early%20meeting%20will%20occur%2C%20but%20naming%20his%20replacement%20will%20ultimately%20fall%20to%20the%20delegates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20delegates%20are%20prepared%20to%20take%20seriously%20their%20responsibility%20in%20swiftly%20delivering%20a%20candidate%20to%20the%20American%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20Harrison%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20%26quot%3Bprocess%20will%20be%20governed%20by%20established%20rules%20and%20procedures%20of%20the%20Party.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20last-minute%20change%20could%20bring%20US%20politics%20back%20to%20the%20old%20days%2C%20when%20party%20bosses%20jostled%20to%20pick%20a%20nominee%20through%20deal-making%20in%20smoke-filled%20back%20rooms%20and%20endless%20rounds%20of%20voting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20March%2031%2C%201968%2C%20then-president%20Lyndon%20Johnson%20made%20the%20shock%20announcement%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20Vietnam%20War%20that%20he%20would%20not%20seek%20reelection.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20move%20--%20though%20announced%20far%20earlier%20in%20the%20campaign%20than%20Biden's%20--%20turned%20that%20year's%20convention%2C%20also%20in%20Chicago%2C%20into%20a%20political%20crisis%2C%20with%20protesters%20in%20the%20streets%20and%20left-leaning%20delegates%20angry%20at%20the%20pro-war%20stance%20of%20party-picked%20candidate%20Hubert%20Humphrey.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20that%20debacle%2C%20states%20more%20widely%20embraced%20the%20primary%20process%20and%20conventions%20have%20become%20well-oiled%20affairs%20whose%20outcomes%20are%20effectively%20known%20in%20advance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20might%20step%20in%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EImmediately%20after%20Biden's%20disastrous%20performance%20against%20Trump%20in%20a%20June%2027%20debate%2C%20which%20supercharged%20the%20concerns%20over%20his%20age%20and%20ability%20to%20beat%20the%20Republican%20at%20the%20polls%2C%20Democrats%20had%20circled%20their%20wagons%20around%20the%20president%20--%20at%20least%20when%20speaking%20on%20the%20record.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20of%20that%20dissolved%20as%20time%20went%20on%2C%20with%20increasingly%20senior%20party%20leaders%20publicly%20questioning%20the%20viability%20of%20the%20incumbent's%20candidacy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20natural%20--%20but%20not%20automatic%20--%20pick%20to%20take%20Biden's%20place%20would%20be%20Vice%20President%20Kamala%20Harris%2C%20whom%20Biden%20quickly%20endorsed%20Sunday%20--%20and%20who%20vowed%20to%20pick%20up%20the%20baton.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWith%20this%20selfless%20and%20patriotic%20act%2C%20President%20Biden%20is%20doing%20what%20he%20has%20done%20throughout%20his%20life%20of%20service%3A%20putting%20the%20American%20people%20and%20our%20country%20above%20everything%20else%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20honored%20to%20have%20the%20president's%20endorsement%20and%20my%20intention%20is%20to%20earn%20and%20win%20this%20nomination....%26quot%3BI%20will%20do%20everything%20in%20my%20power%20to%20unite%20the%20Democratic%20Party%20--%20and%20unite%20our%20nation%20--%20to%20defeat%20Donald%20Trump.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20president%20Bill%20Clinton%20and%20ex-secretary%20of%20state%20Hillary%20Clinton%20also%20threw%20their%20support%20behind%20Harris.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESent%20in%20to%20put%20out%20the%20fire%20after%20Biden's%20lackluster%20performance%20at%20the%20debate%2C%20the%2059-year-old%20conceded%20Biden%20had%20been%20%26quot%3Bslow%20to%20start%26quot%3B%20against%20Trump%20but%20had%20%26quot%3Bfinished%20strong.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOtherwise%2C%20any%20of%20a%20number%20of%20strong%20Democratic%20politicians%20--%20Governors%20Gavin%20Newsom%20of%20California%2C%20Gretchen%20Whitmer%20of%20Michigan%20and%20Josh%20Shapiro%20of%20Pennsylvania%20have%20been%2