ously%20opposed%20the%20legalization%20of%20recreational%20marijuana%20before%20changing%20her%20stance%20in%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20her%202020%20campaign%2C%20Harris%20presented%20a%20plan%20to%20reduce%20the%20prison%20population%20for%20women%20and%20children%20and%20put%20an%20end%20to%20solitary%20confinement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20said%20that%20she%20would%20support%20a%20federal%20standard%20on%20use-of-force%20for%20police%20departments%20and%20proposed%20establishing%20a%20federal%20board%20that%20could%20review%20police%20shootings%2C%20according%20to%20The%20Marshall%20Project.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e31c752f-a387-479a-bec2-89ef1f9f83b2%5C%22%3EEconomy%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHarris%20is%20expected%20to%20tout%20some%20of%20the%20headway%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ethe%20Biden%20administration%20has%20made%20with%20economic%20policies%2C%20including%20Biden's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbiden-throws-support-behind-1-trillion-infrastructure-deal-with-gop-2021-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EInfrastructure%20Deal%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhouse-passes-inflation-reduction-act-sending-it-to-biden-2022-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EInflation%20Reduction%20Act%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20included%20a%20cap%20on%20insulin%20costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20April%2C%20Harris%20announced%20a%20nationwide%20%26quot%3BEconomic%20Opportunity%20Tour%26quot%3B%20to%20promote%20the%20administration's%20progress%20in%20investments%20toward%20small%20businesses%2C%20inflation%2C%20and%20student%20loan%20forgiveness.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPreviously%2C%20Harris%20introduced%20policies%20to%20support%20the%20middle%20class%2C%20such%20as%20a%20%243%2C000%20refundable%20tax%20credit%20for%20those%20making%20%2450%2C000%20or%20less%20a%20year%20and%20a%20%246%2C000%20credit%20to%20couples%20making%20%24100%2C000%20or%20less.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe's%20also%20push