n%20and%20Customs%20Enforcement%20if%20they%20were%20arrested%20or%20accused%20of%20committing%20a%20felony.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELater%20on%2C%20a%20Harris%20campaign%20spokesperson%20told%20CNN%20that%20the%20%26quot%3Bpolicy%20could%20have%20been%20applied%20more%20fairly.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHarris%20said%20she%20wanted%20to%20potentially%20overhaul%20ICE%2C%20criticized%20Trump's%20border%20wall%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bmedieval%20vanity%20project%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20backed%20the%20bipartisan%20border%20security%20deal%20that%20would%20have%20closed%20the%20border%20if%20a%20threshold%20of%205%2C000%20migrants%20a%20week%20was%20reached.%20Senate%20Republicans%20shot%20down%20the%20legislation%20in%20May.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20vice%20president%2C%20Harris%20was%20tasked%20with%20handling%20the%20root%20causes%20of%20migration%20to%20the%20US%20from%20Central%20America.%20In%20a%20move%20which%20angered%20some%20congressional%20Democrats%2C%20Harris%20warned%20migrants%20not%20to%20travel%20to%20the%20US%20border.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDo%20not%20come.%20Do%20not%20come.%20The%20United%20States%20will%20continue%20to%20enforce%20our%20laws%20and%20secure%20our%20borders%2C%26quot%3B%20Harris%20said%20during%20a%202021%20news%20conference%20alongside%20then-Guatemalan%20President%20Alejandro%20Giammattei.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERepublicans%20have%20already%20tried%20to%20inflate%20Harris'%20responsibilities%2C%20deeming%20her%20a%20%26quot%3Bborder%20czar.%26quot%3B%20Polling%20has%20shown%20that%20Trump%20holds%20a%20major%20advantage%20on%20immigration%2C%20illustrating%20why%20the%20GOP%20wants%20to%20saddle%20Harris%20with%20the%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2267fc8e31-4c76-4345-8390-8bb3ce76e25b%5C%22%3EIsrael-Gaza%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20her%202020%20run%2C%20Harris%20was%20a%20strong%20supporter%20of%20the%20US's%20relationship%20with%20Israel%2C%20once%20calling%20it%20an%20%26quot%3Bunbreakable%26quot%3B%20bond%2C%20and%20assured%20that%20she%2