ion%20had%20swirled%20for%20weeks%20regarding%20Biden's%20intentions%20following%20his%20poor%20debate%20performance%20last%20month%2C%20the%20president's%20decision%20is%20still%20stunning%20since%20he%20had%20repeatedly%20insisted%20he%20would%20continue%20his%20reelection%20bid.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20veteran%20of%20Washington%20politics%20for%20more%20than%2050%20years%2C%20Biden%20has%20weathered%20storms%20like%20few%20other%20candidates%20in%20modern%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20he%20met%20his%20match%20in%20former%20House%20Speaker%20Nancy%20Pelosi%2C%20who%20remains%20perhaps%20the%20party's%20most%20important%20political%20strategist%20despite%20having%20ceded%20her%20leadership%20role%20early%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPelosi%20led%20Democratic%20House%20majorities%20from%202007%20to%202011%20and%20from%202019%20to%202023%2C%20anchored%20by%20victories%20in%20critical%20swing%20districts%20across%20the%20country.%20In%20addition%20to%20Pelosi's%20legendary%20whip%20operation%20on%20the%20House%20floors%2C%20she%20has%20a%20keen%20ability%20in%20sensing%20when%20candidates%20are%20in%20trouble%20in%20their%20districts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20in%20data%20taken%20from%20multiple%20pollsters%2C%20Biden%20continued%20to%20trail%20Trump%20after%20the%20debate.%20The%20dynamic%20that%20Biden%20hoped%20to%20reverse%20simply%20hadn't%20changed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPelosi%20privately%20told%20Biden%20and%20several%20colleagues%20that%20she%20found%20it%20incredibly%20difficult%20to%20see%20a%20path%20forward%20for%20his%20candidacy%2C%20according%20to%20The%20New%20York%20Times.%20She%20also%20reportedly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fschumer-jeffries-conversations-biden-staying-in-race-hurts-democrats-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eworked%20behind%20the%20scenes%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20get%20him%20to%20drop%20out.%20Her%20influence%20has%20been%20so%20significant%20that%20Biden%20himself%20considered%20her%20the%20%26quot%3Bmain%20instigator%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20situation%2C%20as%20The%20Times%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbiden-netanyahu-visit-drop-out-nyt-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eput%20it%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20went%20on%20MSNBC's%20%26quot%3BMorning%20Joe%26quot%3B%20(one%20of%20Biden's%20favorite%20programs)%20and%20said%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpelosi-biden-presidential-race-democrats-debate-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eit%20was%20up%20to%20him%20to%20decide%3C%2Fa%3E%20if%20he%20wanted%20to%20stay%20in%20the%20race%2C%20even%20though%20he'd%20already%20clearly%20and%20repeatedly%20said%20he%20was%20staying%20in%20it.%20Notably%2C%20she%20did%20not%20explicitly%20endorse%20Biden%20in%20the%20interview%20and%20said%20%26quot%3Btime%20is%20running%20short%26quot%3B%20for%20him%20to%20make%20a%20decision%2C%20which%2C%20again%2C%20he'd%20already%20made.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHer%20statements%20and%20backroom%20maneuvers%20undoubtedly%20gave%20her%20Democratic%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fadam-schiff-calls-on-biden-drop-out-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econgressional%20colleagues%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20cover%20they%20needed%20to%20call%20for%20Biden%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhich-elected-democrats-called-on-joe-biden-drop-out-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estep%20aside%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPelosi%20is%20a%20Democratic%20Party%20institutionalist%20through%20and%20through.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20has%20worked%20with%20Biden%20for%20decades%2C%20and%20helped%20shepherd%20key%20pieces%20of%20legislation%20like%20the%20bipartisan%20infrastructure%20law%20and%20the%20Inflation%20Reduction%20Act%20through%20the%20House.%20When%20Biden%20served%20as%20vice%20president%20under%20President%20Barack%20Obama%2C%20she%20did%20the%20same%20in%20getting%20the%20Lilly%20Ledbetter%20Fair%20Pay%20Act%20and%20the%20Affordable%20Care%20Act%20through%20Congress%20and%20to%20the%20president's%20desk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPelosi%20has%20long%20touted%20her%20strong%20working%20relationship%20with%20Biden.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20state%20of%20the%202024%20presidential%20campaign%20was%20a%20critical%20crossroads%20that%20Pelosi%20had%20to%20face.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20knew%20that%20Biden%20continued%20to%20falter%20in%20polling%20after%20the%20June%20debate.%20And%20swing-district%20Democrats%2C%20wary%20of%20Biden%20potentially%20tamping%20down%20enthusiasm%20at%20the%20top%20of%20the%20ticket%2C%20clearly%20relayed%20their%20concerns%20to%20her%20about%20his%20standing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPelosi%2C%20long%20known%20for%20her%20blunt%20manner%2C%20didn't%20lead%20the%20House%20Democratic%20Caucus%20for%2020%20years%20by%20accident.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20withdrawing%20from%20the%20race%20and%20backing%20Harris%20to%20succeed%20him%2C%20Biden%20demonstrated%20the%20sort%20of%20passing%20of%20the%20torch%20that%20many%20Democrats%20had%20hoped%20to%20see%20earlier%20in%20his%20term.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20it%20highlighted%20the%20enduring%20power%20of%20Pelosi%2C%20whose%20influence%20continues%20to%20profoundly%20shape%20the%20Democratic%20Party.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbiden-pelosi-lord-almighty-step-aside-election-2024-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721594079000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F669d6a642d66759f66fcbdd7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbiden-pelosi-lord-almighty-step-aside-election-2024-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Biden%20has%20endured%20the%20rough-and-tumble%20arena%20of%20Washington%20politics%20for%20over%2050%20years.%20But%20there's%20perhaps%20no%20greater%20force%20than%20Nancy%20Pelosi.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%