C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fkamala-harris-says-she-will-earn-and-win-democratic-nomination-for-us-president-and-beat-donald-trump%2Famp_articleshow%2F111909293.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22From%20Kamala%20Harris%20To%20Josh%20Shapiro%3A%20Who%20Will%20Replace%20Biden%20In%202024%20Race%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EJoe%20Biden's%20withdrawal%20from%20the%20race%20for%20the%20White%20House%20leaves%20a%20gap%20atop%20the%20Democratic%20presidential%20ticket%20that%20the%20party%20is%20now%20rushing%20to%20fill.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%20is%20a%20look%20at%20potential%20replacements%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EKamala%20Harris%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20seems%20like%20the%20obvious%20choice%2C%20and%20Biden%20has%20given%20her%20his%20endorsement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUS%20Vice%20President%20Kamala%20Harris%2C%20who%20has%20been%20a%20heartbeat%20away%20from%20the%20Oval%20Office%20since%20Biden's%20January%202021%20swearing%20in%2C%20is%20well%20positioned%20to%20be%20the%20Democratic%20Party's%20standard-bearer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2059-year-old%20Harris%2C%20the%20daughter%20of%20a%20Jamaican%20father%20and%20an%20Indian%20mother%2C%20is%20a%20trailblazer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20was%20the%20first%20Black%20person%20and%20the%20first%20woman%20to%20serve%20as%20California's%20attorney%20general%2C%20and%20then%20was%20the%20first%20US%20senator%20of%20South%20Asian%20descent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20is%20now%20the%20first%20woman%20and%20first%20Black%20vice%20president.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20her%20career%20as%20a%20prosecutor%2C%20Harris%20had%20a%20reputation%20for%20being%20tough%20--%20a%20trait%20she%20could%20use%20to%20advantage%20in%20a%20campaign%20expected%20to%20focus%20on%20crime%20and%20immigration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20some%20progressive%20Democrats%20have%20been%20critical%20of%20her%20strict%20punishment%20of%20minor%20offenders%2C%20saying%20it%20disproportionately%20affected%20minorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarris%20also%20suffers%20from%20a%20dismal%20approval%20rating%2C%20which%20could%20prompt%20Democrats%20to%20find%20another%20solution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EGavin%20Newsom%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20no%20rule%20that%20a%20running%20mate%20automatically%20replaces%20the%20presidential%20candidate%20in%20the%20case%20of%20a%20withdrawal.%20This%20is%20why%20California%20Governor%20Gavin%20Newsom's%20name%20keeps%20popping%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2056-year-old%20Democrat%2C%20a%20former%20mayor%20of%20San%20Francisco%2C%20has%20been%20at%20the%20helm%20of%20the%20Golden%20State%20--%20the%20most%20populous%20in%20the%20United%20States%20--%20for%20five%20years%2C%20and%20has%20made%20it%20a%20haven%20for%20abortion%20access.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENewsom%20steadfastly%20supported%20Biden%20and%20dismissed%20talk%20of%20replacing%20him%20prior%20to%20the%20Democrat's%20withdrawal%2C%20but%20he%20has%20also%20made%20little%20secret%20of%20his%20own%20presidential%20ambitions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20recent%20months%2C%20he%20has%20increased%20his%20international%20travel%2C%20run%20multiple%20ads%20touting%20his%20record%2C%20and%20invested%20millions%20of%20dollars%20in%20a%20political%20action%20committee%2C%20fueling%20speculation%20that%20he%20will%20run%20in%202028.%20So%20why%20not%202024%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EGretchen%20Whitmer%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20possible%20Democratic%20candidate%20is%20Gretchen%20Whitmer%2C%20the%2052-year-old%20governor%20of%20Michigan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20state%20has%20both%20a%20strong%20working-class%20population%20and%20major%20Black%20and%20Arab%20American%20communities%20--%20all%20key%20groups%20of%20voters%20that%20Biden%20struggled%20to%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhitmer%2C%20a%20fierce%20critic%20of%20Trump%2C%20is%20perhaps%20best%20known%20for%20being%20the%20intended%20target%20of%20a%20k