0debate%20might%20do%20little%20to%20improve%20his%20chances%20or%20even%20cast%20an%20unflattering%20light%20on%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20Biden%20aides%20thought%20they%20had%20scored%20a%20coup%20in%20agreeing%20to%20a%20June%20debate.%20They%20worked%20with%20broadcaster%20CNN%20to%20shape%20the%20rules%20in%20what%20they%20thought%20was%20their%20favor%20and%20agreed%20on%20May%2015%20to%20two%20debates%2C%20including%20the%20first%20on%20June%2027.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20earlier%20debate%20would%20serve%20Biden%20well%2C%20some%20aides%20thought%2C%20convincing%20voters%20that%20there%20was%20no%20other%20anti-Trump%20option%20in%20the%20race%2C%20but%20also%20cushioning%20the%20blow%20of%20any%20mediocre%20performance%20by%20the%20president.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20format%20-%20no%20audience%20to%20pump%20up%20Trump's%20punchlines%2C%20no%20third-party%20candidates%2C%20moderators%20they%20could%20trust%20and%20a%20mute%20button%20on%20the%20microphones-%20would%2C%20they%20thought%2C%20favor%20Biden's%20style.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EJET%20LAG%20-%20JUNE%204%20TO%2027%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBiden%20flew%20to%20Europe%20twice%20and%20to%20the%20West%20Coast%20over%20a%2014-day%20period%20before%20taking%20just%20a%20few%20days%20to%20rest%20at%20his%20vacation%20home%20in%20Rehoboth%20Beach%2C%20Delaware.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBiden%20was%20tired%20and%20dragging%20by%20the%20end%20of%20the%20travel%2C%20according%20to%20several%20people%20who%20observed%20him%20during%20this%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20and%20his%20aides%20headed%20to%20Camp%20David%20for%20focused%20prep%20sessions%20on%20June%2021%2C%20where%20they%20peppered%20Biden%20with%20details%2C%20then%20followed%20up%20with%20mock%20debates%20for%20the%20better%20part%20of%20seven%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20BAD%20NIGHT%20-%20JUNE%2027%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20CNN's%20Atlanta%20studios%2C%20Biden%20stumbled%20over%20his%20words%20and%20lost%20his%20train%20of%20thought.%20His%20delivery%2C%20appearance%20and%20voice%20drew%20the%20immediate%20attention%20of%20reporters%2C%20who%20asked%20his%20aides%20for%20an%20explanation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOfficials%20told%20reporters%20as%20the%20debate%20was%20underway%20some%20new%20information%3A%20Biden%20was%20sick%20with%20a%20cold%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBiden's%20hoarseness%20would%20improve%20as%20the%20debate%20went%20on%20but%20his%20disjointed%20answers%20took%20voters%2C%20donors%20and%20Democratic%20officials%20by%20surprise.%20One%20Democratic%20strategist%20called%20it%20%26quot%3Ba%20disaster.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%2C%2078%2C%20repeated%20a%20series%20of%20well-worn%2C%20glaring%20falsehoods%20during%20the%2090-minute%20debate%2C%20including%20claims%20that%20he%20actually%20had%20won%20the%202020%20election.%20Biden%20failed%20to%20refute%20them%2C%20leaving%20sentences%20and%20thoughts%20unfinished.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20jabbed%20Biden%20for%20being%20incoherent%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20really%20don't%20know%20what%20he%20said%20at%20the%20end%20of%20that%20sentence.%20I%20don't%20think%20he%20knows%20what%20he%20said.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFALLOUT%20-%20JUNE%2027%20TO%20JULY%202%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20know%20I'm%20not%20a%20young%20man%2C%20to%20state%20the%20obvious%2C%26quot%3B%20Biden%20said%20the%20day%20after%20the%20debate%2C%20admitting%20a%20poor%20performance.%20%26quot%3BNearly%20fell%20asleep%20on%20stage%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20on%20July%202.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECalls%20for%20Biden%20to%20step%20down%20would%20start%20in%20the%20hours%20after%20the%20debate.%20Calls%20from%20Biden%20aides%20to%20worried%20Democrats%20facing%20reelection%20campaigns%20who%20saw%20their%20political%20futures%20flashing%20before%20their%20eyes%2C%20wouldn't%20start%20until%20days%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20lawmakers%20started%20to%20break%20ranks%2C%20starting%20with%20US%20Representative%20Lloyd%20Doggett%20on%20July%202%2C%20and%20then%20gathering%20steam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAngry%20donors%20told%20Biden's%20aides%20they%20would%20need%20to%20see%20a%20turnaround%20in%20the%20candidate's%20performance.%20Senior%20Democrats%20and%20Biden%20allies%20also%20began%20to%20hint%20at%20changes%20to%20the%20ticket.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHouse%20of%20Representatives%20Democrat%20Jim%20Clyburn%20-%20a%20kingmaker%20of%20sorts%20within%20the%20Democratic%20Party%20who%20was%20instrumental%20in%20Biden's%202020%20win%20-%20said%20on%20July%202%20that%20he%20would%20back%20Vice%20President%20Kamala%20Harris%20if%20Biden%20did%20depart%20and%20suggested%20the%20idea%20of%20a%20%26quot%3Bmini-primary%26quot%3B%20if%20Biden%20stepped%20aside.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20House%20Speaker%20Nancy%20Pelosi%2C%20a%20longtime%20Biden%20ally%2C%20said%20it%20was%20legitimate%20to%20ask%20whether%20Biden's%20performance%20in%20Atlanta%20was%20an%20%26quot%3Bepisode%26quot%3B%20or%20a%20condition.%20She%20also%20hinted%20that%20Biden%20would%20need%20to%20examine%20his%20choice%20to%20say%20in%20the%20race.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETHE%20DAM%20BREAKS%20-%20JULY%205%20TO%208%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBiden%20would%20fail%20to%20quiet%20the%20chorus%20of%20dissent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20first%20major%20interview%20after%20the%20debate%2C%20on%20July%205%2C%20Biden%20told%20ABC%20News%20anchor%20George%20Stephanopoulos%20that%20only%20the%20%26quot%3BLord%20Almighty%26quot%3B%20could%20cast%20him%20from%20the%20race.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20worrying%20to%20some%20Democrats%2C%20Biden%20said%20he%20could%20accept%20remaining%20in%20the%20race%20and%20losing%20to%20Trump%20%26quot%3Bas%20long%20as%20I%20gave%20it%20my%20all%20and%20I%20did%20as%20good%20a%20job%20as%20I%20know%20I%20can%20do.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThirty-six%20Democratic%20U.S.%20lawmakers%20and%20one%20independent%20who%20caucuses%20with%20the%20Democrats%20would%20ultimately%20call%20for%20Biden%20to%20step%20off%20the%20ticket%20over%20the%2024%20days%20that%20followed%20the%20debate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENATO%2C%20POLLS%20-%20JULY%209%20TO%2012%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBiden%20tried%20to%20move%20on.%20He%20gave%20interviews%2C%20held%20a%20press%20conference%20and%20gave%20stern%20speeches%20on%20the%20campaign%20trail%20as%20well%20as%20at%20the%20NATO%20summit%20of%20US%20allies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20events%20sometimes%20raised%20more%20concerns%20than%20they%20quieted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20NATO%20summit%20during%20the%20second%20week%20of%20July%2C%20Biden%20mixed%20up%20the%20names%20of%20his%20vice%20president%20Harris%20and%20his%20Republican%20rival%20Trump%2C%20and%20those%20of%20Ukrainian%20President%20Volodymyr%20Zelensky%20and%20Russian%20President%20Vladimir%20Putin%2C%20whose%20countries%20are%20at%20war%20with%20each%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolls%20showed%20Biden%20trailing%20other%20Democrats%20in%20many%20of%20the%20key%20states%20and%20districts%20Democrats%20need%20to%20win%20in%20November%2C%20though%20polls%20nationwide%20continued%20to%20point%20to%20a%20close%20race.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBiden%20was%20unmoved%2C%20still%20believing%20he%20was%20the%20best%20candidate%20to%20face%20Trump%2C%20that%20he%20could%20rebound%20from%20this%20setback%20as%20he%20has%20so%20many%20times%20before%2C%20a%20view%20reinforced%20by%20a%20close%20circle%20of%20aides.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETRUMP%20RALLY%20SHOOTING%20-%20JULY%2013%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20was%20shot%20while%20giving%20a%20speech%20in%20Pennsylvania.%20The%20bullet%20grazed%20his%20ear%2C%20bloodied%20his%20face%2C%20and%20photos%20of%20the%20former%20president%20holding%20up%20his%20fist%20in%20defiance%20were%20shown%20widely.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERepublicans%20spoke%20of%20divine%20providence%2C%20unifying%20around%20their%20candidate.%20Democrats%2