20Biden's%20withdrawal%20upends%20what%20was%20already%20a%20White%20House%20race%20for%20the%20ages%2C%20but%20it%20will%20rattle%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20too%20--%20forcing%20him%20to%20recalibrate%20a%20campaign%20that%20was%20focused%20almost%20entirely%20on%20his%20former%20opponent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20months%20Trump%20and%20his%20allies%20have%20been%20playing%20on%20concerns%20that%20the%2081-year-old%20Biden%20may%20no%20longer%20be%20fit%20for%20office%2C%20gleefully%20sharing%20video%20clips%20of%20every%20stammer%2C%20rhetorical%20gaffe%20and%20red%20carpet%20stumble.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20frequently%20a%20target%20of%20Republican%20mockery%20and%20scorn%20at%20the%20Republican%20National%20Convention%20in%20Milwaukee%2C%20where%20Trump's%20newly%20announced%20running%20mate%20J.D.%20Vance%20called%20him%20%26quot%3BFake%20Scranton%20Joe.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20with%20the%20Democrat%20no%20longer%20in%20the%20race%2C%20the%20Trump%20operation%20finds%20itself%20pushed%20into%20a%20strategic%20pivot%2C%20forced%20now%20to%20shift%20its%20messaging%20to%20fit%20a%20contest%20with%20no%20incumbent%20and%20a%20yet-to-be-confirmed%20opponent%2C%20although%20Biden%20did%20endorse%20Vice%20President%20Kamala%20Harris%20on%20Sunday%20as%20he%20pulled%20out%20of%20the%20race.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBiden%20withdrawing%20is%20bad%20news%20for%20Trump%2C%26quot%3B%20Henry%20Olsen%2C%20a%20senior%20fellow%20at%20the%20conservative%20Ethics%20and%20Public%20Policy%20Center%20think%20tank%2C%20told%20AFP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBiden%20has%20the%20lowest%20job%20approval%20of%20any%20first-term%20president%20at%20this%20stage%20of%20his%20presidency%20in%20polling%20history%20and%20is%20also%20irretrievably%20burdened%20by%20his%20age.%20It's%20much%20better%20for%20Trump%20to%20run%20against%20him%20than%20any%20conceivable%20opponent.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrumpworld%20had%20been%20playing%20down%20the%20chances%20of%20Biden%20withdrawing%2C%20but%20behind%20the%20scenes%20aides%20have%20been%20consumed%20by%20the%20contingencies%2C%20preparing%20a%20brutal%20assault%20on%20the%20veteran%20Democrat's%20heir%20apparent%2C%20Harris.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNothing%20fundamentally%20changes%26quot%3B%20Jason%20Miller%2C%20one%20of%20Trump's%20closest%20advisors%2C%20told%20AFP%20during%20the%20Republican%20convention%2C%20saying%20that%20any%20%26quot%3Bradical%20liberal%26quot%3B%20Democratic%20opponent%2C%20Harris%20or%20otherwise%2C%20shares%20%26quot%3Bthe%20responsibility%20for%20the%20failure%20of%20destroying%20our%20economy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarris%2C%20a%2059-year-old%20former%20California%20senator%20is%20not%20a%20shoo-in%2C%20and%20could%20face%20competition%20from%20multiple%20leading%20Democrats%20in%20Congress%20and%20the%20nation's%2023%20Democratic%20governors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20going%20to%20show%20up%20and%20I'm%20going%20to%20campaign%20--%20whether%20it's%20him%20or%20somebody%20else%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20told%20a%20radio%20network%20in%20Virginia%20before%20Biden's%20announcement%2C%20pointing%20to%20polls%20showing%20him%20doing%20as%20well%20or%20better%20against%20other%20Democrats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E-%20Clash%20of%20cultures%20-%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVoters%20have%20been%20telling%20pollsters%20for%20months%20they%20want%20younger%20political%20leaders%2C%20and%20a%20ticket%20topped%20by%20a%20relatively%20youthful%20swing%20state%20governor%2C%20for%20example%2C%20would%20be%20a%20threat%20to%20Trump%2C%20who%20would%20be%2082%20at%20the%20end%20of%20a%20second%20term.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20campaign%20led%20by%20Harris%20and%20backed%20up%20by%20a%20moderate%20midwestern%20running%20mate%20could%20present%20the%20biggest%20danger%20though%2C%20helping%20turn%20out%20more%20women%2C%20who%20historically%20vote%20in%20greater%20numbers%20than%20men%20and%20are%20a%20weakness%20for%20Trump.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarris%20would%20also%20give%20Democrats%20a%20chance%20to%20redefine%20the%20race%20at%20their%20convention%20in%20Chicago%20in%20August%20as%20a%20clash%20of%20cultures%20between%20a%20former%20prosecutor%20and%20a%20convicted%20felon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20Harris%20ensures%20that%20abortion%20rights%20--%20one%20of%20her%20biggest%20domestic%20priorities%20and%20another%20vulnerability%20for%20Trump%20and%20the%20Republicans%20--%20remains%20a%20crucial%20election%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump's%20new%2C%20serious%20focus%20on%20the%20vice%20president%20was%20demonstrated%20by%20his%20bestowal%20on%20her%20of%20one%20of%20his%20famous%20nicknames%2C%20referring%20to%20her%20on%20social%20media%20recently%20as%20%26quot%3BLaffin'%20Kamala%20Harris.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E-%20'Destruction%20and%20chaos'%20-%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20the%20disastrous%20June%20presidential%20debate%20in%20Atlanta%20that%20proved%20the%20catalyst%20for%20Biden's%20withdrawal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20new%20survey%20from%20Democratic%20polling%20form%20Public%20Policy%20Polling%20released%20Thursday%20found%20that%20Harris%20--%20with%20the%20right%20running%20mate%20--%20likely%20can%20defeat%20Trump%20and%20Vance%20in%20Pennsylvania%20and%20Michigan%2C%20two%20of%20the%20three%20%26quot%3BBlue%20Wall%26quot%3B%20states%20seen%20as%20critical%20to%20electing%20a%20Democratic%20president.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20vice%20president%20has%20the%20disadvantage%20of%20incumbency%2C%20though%2C%20meaning%20Trump%20can%20pin%20on%20her%20anything%20that%20was%20considered%20a%20weakness%20for%20Biden%20--%20including%20the%20border%20crisis%2C%20on%20which%20Harris%20led%20the%20administration's%20early%20efforts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20Democratic%20rising%20stars%20have%20been%20floated%20as%20alternatives%2C%20including%20governors%20Josh%20Shapiro%2C%20Gretchen%20Whitmer%20and%20Gavin%20Newsom.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENewsom%2C%20of%20California%20--%20who%20has%20demonstrated%