ieve%20it%20is%20in%20the%20best%20interest%20of%20my%20party%20and%20the%20country%20for%20me%20to%20stand%20down%20and%20focus%20solely%20on%20fulfilling%20my%20duties%20as%20President%20for%20the%20remainder%20of%20my%20term.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBiden%20said%20he%20would%20%26quot%3Bspeak%20to%20the%20nation%20later%20this%20week%20in%20more%20detail%20about%20my%20decision.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Democratic%20Party%20is%20now%20plunged%20into%20chaos%20and%20needs%20to%20find%20a%20new%20candidate%20by%20November's%20election%2C%20with%20Vice%20President%20Kamala%20Harris%20the%20frontrunner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20stunning%20move%20makes%20Biden%20the%20first%20president%20in%20US%20history%20to%20pull%20out%20so%20late%20in%20an%20election%20race%2C%20and%20the%20first%20to%20bow%20out%20because%20of%20concerns%20over%20his%20mental%20acuity%20and%20health.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBiden%20spent%20more%20than%20three%20weeks%20resisting%20calls%20to%20step%20down%20following%20the%20shock%20of%20the%20June%2027%20debate%2C%20at%20one%20point%20insisting%20that%20only%20the%20%26quot%3BLord%20Almighty%26quot%3B%20could%20convince%20him%20to%20back%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20bid%20to%20show%20he%20was%20up%20to%20the%20job%2C%20he%20gave%20a%20number%20of%20interviews%20and%20what%20was%20billed%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bbig%20boy%26quot%3B%20press%20conference%20in%20which%20he%20took%20numerous%20questions%2C%20but%20made%20further%20gaffes%20including%20calling%20Kamala%20Harris%20%26quot%3BVice%20President%20Trump.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20tide%20of%20voices%20within%20his%20own%20party%20calling%20on%20him%20to%20go%2C%20starting%20with%20donor%20and%20actor%20George%20Clooney%20and%20ending%20with%20former%20president%20Barack%20Obama%2C%20sealed%20his%20fate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20end%20finally%20came%20shortly%20after%20Biden%20had%20been%20diagnosed%20with%20Covid%2C%20forcing%20him%20off%20the%20campaign%20trail%20