Capitol%20assault%20by%20his%20supporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOvercoming%20a%20reputation%20for%20verbal%20flubs%2C%20Barack%20Obama's%20former%20vice%20president%20pushed%20through%20a%20massive%20Covid%20recovery%20plan%20and%20a%20green%20industry%20scheme.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUS%20allies%20welcomed%20his%20pledge%20that%20%26quot%3BAmerica%20is%20back%26quot%3B%20following%20Trump's%20trampling%20on%20international%20alliances%2C%20and%20his%20strong%20support%20for%20Ukraine%20as%20it%20battled%20Russia's%202022%20invasion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20he%20faced%20criticism%20over%20the%20catastrophic%20US%20withdrawal%20from%20Afghanistan%20and%20inflation%20that%20meant%20overstretched%20Americans%20ignored%20otherwise%20positive%20economic%20numbers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBehind%20it%20all%20were%20the%20ongoing%20concerns%20about%20his%20age%20with%20a%20series%20of%20senior%20moments%2C%20including%20tripping%20up%20the%20stairs%20to%20Air%20Force%20One%20and%20falling%20off%20his%20bike%2C%20contributing%20to%20the%20doddery%20image%20played%20up%20by%20Republicans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721587140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fpn27j9kg_joe-biden-_625x300_12_July_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fjoe-biden-drops-out-of-us-presidential-election-race-says-it-is-in-best-interest-of-country-for-me-to-stand-down-6156671%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22US%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20announced%20Sunday%20that%20he%20was%20dropping%20out%20of%20his%20reelection%20battle%20with%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20in%20a%20historic%20move%20that%20plunges%20the%20already%20turbulent%202024%20White%20House%20race%20into%20uncharted%20territory.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%