0and%20his%20family%20fled%20from%20this%20Kuki%20tribes-dominated%20area%20when%20ethnic%20violence%20broke%20out%20in%20May%202023.%20Today%2C%20Mr%20Ibomcha%20said%2C%20he%20saw%20a%20viral%20video%20of%20his%20four-storey%20house%20in%20Churachandpur%20razed%20to%20the%20ground%20in%20a%20massive%2C%20surgical%20explosion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYes%2C%20that's%20our%20house.%20We%20were%20a%20joint%20family%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Ibomcha%20told%20NDTV.%20%26quot%3BIn%20September%20last%20year%2C%20a%20friend%20in%20the%20aid%20services%20told%20me%20the%20house%20my%20family%20built%20had%20been%20demolished%20by%20the%20Kukis.%20This%20is%20the%20first%20time%20I%20am%20seeing%20the%20video%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20and%20choked%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Ibomcha%20said%20he%20doesn't%20know%20when%20exactly%20the%20bombing%20happened%2C%20but%20it%20was%20definitely%20between%20May%20and%20September%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20video%20shows%20the%20four-storey%20house%20being%20blasted%20surgically%20with%20explosives%20strapped%20to%20the%20pillars%2C%20indicating%20the%20alleged%20involvement%20of%20hands%20trained%20in%20specialised%20demolition%20activity.%20Some%20voices%20are%20heard%20talking%20in%20the%20Paite%20tribes%20dialect.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20his%20family%20ran%20a%20licenced%20gun%20shop%20for%20eight%20years%2C%20until%20May%203%20-%20the%20day%20clashes%20erupted%20-%20when%20Kuki%20rioters%20barged%20in%2C%20vandalised%20the%20store%2C%20and%20looted%20the%20weapons.%20Mobile%20videos%20and%20CCTV%20camera%20footage%20from%20the%20shop%20show%20the%20mob%20ransacking%20the%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20gun%20shop%20owner%20was%20detained%20by%20the%20Assam%20Rifles%20in%20June%202019%20while%20transporting%20advanced%20rifle%20scopes%20from%20the%20border%20trading%20town%20Moreh%20to%20Imphal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22