20in%20Mandop%20Leikai%2C%20was%20horrified%20to%20see%20a%20flattened%20plot%20of%20land%20where%20his%20house%20stood.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Ibomcha%20alleged%20the%20security%20forces%20could%20have%20easily%20stopped%20the%20mass%20demolition%20of%20Meitei%20houses%20in%20Churachandpur.%20%26quot%3BWhat%20was%20most%20heartbreaking%20was%20the%20security%20forces%20didn't%20do%20anything%20to%20prevent%20this%20systematic%20demolition...%26quot%3B%20he%20alleged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Churachandpur%20MLA%2C%20LM%20Khuate%2C%20is%20a%20former%20DGP%20(Director%20General%20of%20Police)%2C%20and%20the%20DGP%20in%20May%202023%20was%20another%20officer%20from%20the%20Kuki%20tribes%2C%20P%20Doungel.%20I%20am%20sure%20had%20they%20wanted%2C%20they%20could%20have%20prevented%20the%20demolition%20of%20my%20house%20and%20all%20other%20properties%20of%20Meitei%20families%20in%20Churachandpur%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Ibomcha%20alleged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20Meitei%20community%20claims%20nearly%20all%20properties%20in%20the%20state%20capital%20Imphal%2C%20a%20valley%20area%2C%20owned%20by%20the%20Kuki%20tribes%20remain%20standing%20under%20the%20watch%20of%20the%20security%20forces%2C%20the%20Kuki%20tribes%20and%20their%20civil%20society%20organisations%20say%20their%20community%20suffered%20more%20casualties%2C%20lived%20through%20intense%20harassment%20and%20hounding%20by%20Meitei%20mobs%20when%20the%20clashes%20began.%20The%20Kukis%20claim%20nearly%20all%20their%20properties%20in%20Imphal%20were%20destroyed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fvkl1bcig_churachandpur_625x300_23_September_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20Kuki%20houses%20in%20Imphal%20have%20been%20occupied%20by%20Meitei%20armed%20groups%2C%20according%20to%20Kuki%20civil%