0faith%20mocked%2C%20and%20their%20way%20of%20life%20disrespected.%20Kuki%20miscreants%20would%20call%20names%20to%20Meiteis%20living%20in%20Churachandpur%2C%20deny%20access%20to%20markets%2C%20not%20allow%20Meitei%20families%20to%20run%20small%20shops%2C%20take%20goods%20by%20force%20and%20not%20pay%2C%20apart%20from%20two%20dozen%20Kuki%20terrorist%20groups%20taking%20illegal%20taxes%20from%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Ibomcha%20said%20in%20the%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELand%20Records%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManipur%20government%20records%20show%20there%20are%2018%20villages%20in%20Churachandpur%20that%20fall%20under%20revenue%20areas.%20The%20Meitei%20community%20living%20in%20these%20villages%20say%20they%20hold%20land%20%26quot%3Bpattas%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20revenue%20areas%2C%20and%20so%20claims%20by%20a%20section%20of%20the%20Kukis%20that%20Meiteis%20have%20no%20land%20ownership%20in%20hill%20areas%20is%20simply%20not%20true%20since%20these%20claims%20ignore%20the%20nuances.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMeiteis%20have%20been%20living%20in%20Churachandpur%20for%20decades%20before%20the%20land%20revenue%20law%20came.%20Their%20rights%20as%20legal%20patta-dars%20continue%20even%20after%20imposition%20of%20the%20law.%20And%20it%20happened%20that%20the%20Meiteis%20occupied%20the%20prime%20locations%20in%20%5BChurachandpur%5D%20town%2C%20so%20they%20were%20the%20first%20target%20of%20the%20cleansing%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20expert%20in%20Manipur's%20complex%20land%20laws%20told%20NDTV%2C%20requesting%20anonymity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Ffba1hn08_imphal-generic_625x300_26_March_24.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManipur%20is%20geographically%20divided%20into%20hill%20and%20valley%20regions.%20The%20land%20system%20comprises%20s