%20in%20the%201971%20war%20for%20independence%20from%20Pakistan%2C%20followed%20similar%20student%20protests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20suspended%20the%20high%20court%20order%20after%20the%20government's%20appeal.%20On%20Sunday%20it%20dismissed%20the%20lower%20court%20order%20and%20directed%20that%2093%25%20of%20jobs%20should%20be%20open%20to%20candidates%20on%20merit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20reserved%205%25%20of%20jobs%20for%20family%20members%20of%20independence%20fighters%20and%202%25%20for%20people%20from%20so-called%20backward%20groups%20and%20the%20disabled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20students%20had%20stepped%20up%20their%20protest%20when%20Hasina%20refused%20to%20meet%20their%20demands%2C%20citing%20the%20court%20proceedings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20called%20the%20protesters%20%26quot%3Brazakar%26quot%3B%2C%20an%20offensive%20term%20for%20those%20accused%20of%20collaborating%20with%20Pakistan's%20army%20in%201971%20to%20betray%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWHAT%20IS%20THE%20QUOTA%20SYSTEM%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIntroduced%20in%201972%2C%20Bangladesh's%20quota%20system%20has%20gone%20through%20several%20changes%20since.%20When%20it%20was%20abolished%20in%202018%2C%2056%25%20of%20government%20jobs%20were%20blocked%20under%20various%20quotas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bulk%20covered%20groups%20such%20as%20freedom%20fighters'%20families%2C%20with%20women%20and%20those%20from%20underdeveloped%20districts%20receiving%20a%20share%20of%20a%20tenth%20each%2C%20with%205%25%20allotted%20to%20indigenous%20communities%2C%20and%201%25%20for%20the%20disabled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20protesting%20students%20want%20all%20categories%20abolished%2C%20except%20the%20last%20two.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWHAT%20SPARKED%20THE%20VIOLENCE%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20protests%20turned%20violent%20last%20week%20following%20clashes%20between%20thousands%20of%20anti-quota%20demonstrators%20and%20members%20of%20the%20student%20wing%20of%20Hasina's%20Awami%20League%20party.%20Police%20fired%20rubber%20bullets%20and%20hurled%20sound%20grenades%20and%20tear%20gas%20to%20scatter%20protesters%20who%20also%20blocked%20railway%20tracks%20and%20major%20roads.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWHAT%20DO%20THE%20STUDENTS%20FEAR%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHasina%20is%20the%20daughter%20of%20Sheikh%20Mujibur%20Rahman%2C%20the%20founding%20father%20of%20Bangladesh%2C%20who%20led%20its%20freedom%20movement.%20Protesters%20and%20critics%20say%20the%2030%25%20quota%20for%20families%20of%20freedom%20fighters%20favours%20Awami%20League%20supporters%2C%20which%20led%20the%20independence%20fight.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExperts%20also%20attribute%20the%20unrest%20to%20stagnant%20job%20growth%20in%20the%20private%20sector%2C%20making%20public%20sector%20jobs%2C%20with%20their%20accompanying%20regular%20wage%20hikes%20and%20privileges%2C%20very%20attractive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20quotas%20shrink%20the%20number%20of%20government%20jobs%20open%20for%20all%2C%20hurting%20aspirants%20who%20want%20them%20filled%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20merit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20have%20sparked%20anger%20among%20students%20grappling%20with%20high%20youth%20unemployment%2C%20as%20nearly%2032%20million%20young%20people%20are%20out%20of%20work%20or%20education%20in%20a%20population%20of%20170%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20economy%2C%20once%20among%20the%20world's%20fastest-growing%2C%20has%20stagnated%2C%20inflation%20hovers%20around%2010%25%20and%20dollar%20reserves%20are%20shrinking.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWHAT%20HAS%20HASINA%20SAID%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20protests%20are%20the%20first%20challenge%20to%20Hasina's%20government%20since%20she%20won%20a%20fourth%20consecutive%20term%20in%20January%20in%20elections%20boycotted%20by%20the%20main%20opposition.%20She%20has%20condemned%20the%20loss%20of%20lives%20and%20called%20for%20patience%20ahead%20of%20th