ators%20to%20solve%20the%20cases%20fast%20and%20reach%20a%20conclusion%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20every%20case%2C%20Sama%20charges%20one%20percent%20of%20the%20claim%20amounts%20in%20the%20case.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20the%20dispute%20is%20within%20a%C2%A0%20lakh%2C%20we%20charge%20the%20client%20Rs%201%2C000%2C%20whereas%20we%20take%20Rs%202%2C000%20for%20clients%20between%20Rs%201-3%20lakh.%20This%20is%2099%20percent%20cheaper%20than%20the%20courts%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarly%20this%20year%2C%20Sama%20was%20featured%20in%20the%20Shark%20Tank%20India%20season%203%20and%20bagged%20a%20deal%20of%20Rs%201%20crore%20from%20boAt%20co-founder%20Aman%20Gupta%2C%20Namita%20Thapar%2C%20the%20executive%20director%20of%20Emcure%20Pharmaceuticals%2C%20and%20Ritesh%20Agarwal%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20OYO%20Rooms.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNot%20only%20did%20we%20receive%20the%20funding%20but%20this%20exposure%20also%20helped%20us%20get%20a%20good%20reach%20and%20spread%20awareness%20about%20ODR.%20Our%20idea%20got%20a%20validation%20when%20we%20explained%20it%20to%20the%20viewers%20in%20a%20non-legal%20language.%20Finally%2C%20our%20families%20also%20understood%20what%20we%20were%20trying%20to%20do%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20laughs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELooking%20at%20the%20success%20of%20the%20startup%2C%20Pranjal%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CPersonally%2C%20it%20has%20been%20a%20very%20challenging%20but%20rewarding%20journey%20for%20us.%20I%20really%20feel%20Sama%20is%20a%20divine%20%3Cem%3Esewa%20%3C%2Fem%3E(service).%20Every%20day%2C%20we%20deal%20with%20a%20lot%20of%20negativity%20but%20when%20years%20long%20disputes%20are%20solved%2C%20we%20get%20equal%20amounts%20of%20satisfaction.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20will%20take%20us%20another%2010%20years%20to%20make%20Sama%20a%20primary%20resort%20for%20civil%20disputes%20to%20be%20able%20to%20reduce%20the%20burden%20on%20courts%20so%20that%20they%20can%20focus%20on%20criminal%20cases%