%20they%20run%20the%20Adiem%20Kaanan%20Farmstay%20in%20Nashik.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Krystelle%20Dsouza%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F356881%2Fnashik-farmstay-adiem-kaanan-madhu-disha-sustainable-homestay-made-of-bamboo-mud-grape-fields%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98The%20Solution%20Was%20Simple%E2%80%99%3A%20How%20an%20IAS%20Officer%20Revived%20Varanasi%E2%80%99s%20Water%20Table%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20office%20of%20the%20Chief%20Development%20Officer%20(CDO)%20in%20Varanasi%2C%20several%20private%20companies%20responded%20to%20a%20notice%20regarding%20their%20water%20usage.%20For%20years%2C%20these%20companies%20had%20been%20extracting%20groundwater%20without%20replenishing%20it.%20They%20were%20expected%20to%20install%20rooftop%20rainwater%20harvesting%20(RWH)%20systems%20to%20recharge%20aquifers%20as%20they%20continue%20to%20extract%20groundwater.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20private%20companies%20were%20concerned%20about%20the%20lack%20of%20space%20for%20rainwater%20harvesting%20systems%2C%20the%20CDO%20of%20Varanasi%2C%20Himanshu%20Nagpal%2C%20was%20discussing%20with%20a%20local%20college%20principal%20the%20issue%20of%20waterlogging%20on%20campus%20during%20the%20monsoon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20simple%20solution%20to%20both%20issues%20lay%20right%20before%20me.%20By%20installing%20rainwater%20harvesting%20structures%20on%20the%20rooftops%20of%20public%20buildings%20like%20schools%20and%20colleges%2C%20private%20companies%20could%20resolve%20the%20problems%20of%20waterlogging%20on%20campus%20and%20the%20space%20constraints%20for%20rainwater%20harvesting%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%2027-year-old%20IAS%20officer%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20department%20proposed%20the%20solution%20to%20the%20stakeholders%20and%20set%20out%20to%20create%20a%20list%20of%20such%20public%20buildings%20that%20required%20rooftop%20rainwater%20harvesting%20systems.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENearly%20a%20year%20and%20a%20half%20ago%2C%20Himanshu%20observed%20a%20significant%20discrepancy%20in%20the%20district%E2%80%99s%20groundwater%20extraction%20permits.%20The%20district%20received%20only%20about%2030%20No%20Objection%20Certificates%20(NOCs)%20annually%20for%20groundwater%20extraction%2C%20despite%20reports%20of%20at%20least%20700%20borewells%20and%20submersibles%20being%20constructed%20each%20year.%20%E2%80%9CEven%20those%20who%20took%20a%20NOC%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20set%20up%20rainwater%20harvesting%20structures%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20points%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fvaranasi-1721270245.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Himanshu%20shares%20at%20least%201%2C000%20public%20buildings%20including%20schools%20are%20now%20equipped%20with%20rooftop%20rainwater%20harvesting%20systems.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fvaranasi-1721270245.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fvaranasi-1721270245-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fvaranasi-1721270245-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fvaranasi-1721270245-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fvaranasi-1721270245-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-357471%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EHimanshu%20shares%20that%20at%20least%201%2C000%20public%20buildings%20including%20schools%20are%20now%20equipped%20with%20rooftop%20rainwater%20harvesting%20systems.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcgwa-noc.gov.in%2Flandingpage%2FGuidlines%2FConsolidateGuidline.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EConsolidated%20MoJS%20Guidelines%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20regulate%20and%20control%20groundwater%20extraction%20in%20India%2C%20the%20proponent%20(the%20party%20who%20has%20the%20legal%20right%20to%20carry%20out%20a%20project)%20is%20required%20to%20adopt%20rooftop%20rainwater%20harvesting%2Frecharge%20in%20the%20project%20premises.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHimanshu%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CPeople%20have%20been%20digging%20borewells%20and%20installing%20submersibles%20in%20homes%2C%20hotels%2C%20and%20commercial%20buildings.%20They%20are%20required%20to%20obtain%20permission%20from%20the%20district%20administration%20and%2C%20within%20a%20year%2C%20set%20up%20structures%20to%20replenish%20an%20equal%20amount%20of%20water%20through%20their%20rooftops.%20However%2C%20this%20regulation%20is%20not%20being%20followed%20anywhere.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20district%20administration%20identified%20such%20organisations%20after%20conducting%20a%20survey%20of%201%2C435%20borewells%20constructed%20in%20commercial%20premises.%20Soon%2C%20notices%20were%20issued%20to%20them.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20led%20to%20the%20sealing%20of%20150%20borewells%20and%20the%20disconnection%20of%20their%20power%20connections.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20we%20received%20at%20least%20800%20applications%20for%20NOCs.%20After%20speaking%20with%20the%20applicants%2C%20I%20learned%20that%20they%20lacked%20sufficient%20space%20to%20harvest%20rainwater%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20IAS%20officer%20provided%20an%20alternative%20option%20of%20constructing%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F192106%2Fbengaluru-rainwater-harvesting-school-save-water-environment-india%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20targe