%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20inspiring%20endeavour%20to%20tackle%20groundwater%20depletion%20in%20Varanasi%2C%20Himanshu%20adopted%20a%20comprehensive%20water%20rejuvenation%20project%20that%20includes%20a%20multitude%20of%20innovative%20strategies%20to%20increase%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F243812%2Fias-hero-water-able-raising-method-dam-how-management-government-curriculum-ananthagiri-rajrajeshwara-dam-him16%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewater%20table%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20significant%20steps%20taken%20has%20been%20the%20introduction%20of%20393%20%E2%80%98Amrit%20Sarovar%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%94%20artificial%20ponds%20spread%20across%20one-acre%20plots%20intended%20for%20water%20harvesting%2C%20with%20an%20additional%2050%20currently%20under%20construction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAnother%20pivotal%20initiative%20has%20been%20the%20rehabilitation%20of%20the%20Nad%20river%20under%20the%20Nad%20River%20Rejuvenation%20project.%20The%20river%20had%20become%20a%20%3Cem%3Enala%20%3C%2Fem%3E(dirty%20drain)%20as%20it%20would%20receive%20pollutants%20from%20nearby%20industries.%20We%20revived%20the%20river%20through%20extensive%20cleanup%20efforts%20over%20a%2030%20km%20stretch%20and%20the%20development%20of%20ancillary%20ponds%20and%20check%20dams%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20the%20IAS%20officer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COnce%20near%20extinction%2C%20the%20river%20now%20flourishes.%20This%20has%20significantly%20mitigated%20the%20incidence%20of%20waterborne%20diseases%20and%20provided%20reliable%20water%20sources%20for%20irrigation%20and%20domestic%20use%20in%2039%20%3Cem%3Egram%20panchayats%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20this%2C%20the%20IAS%20officer%20also%20integrated%20water-soak%20pits%20around%206%2C000%20handpumps%20to%20ensure%20that%20excess%20water%20filters%20into%20the%20ground%2C%20sub